ygData.subject: Re: SOW rings?
ygData.msgSnippet: I am starting to remember a bit more now.  I think there are 2 quests there - one with the Marshall or Sheriff and the other with the Druid who grows the jum
ygData.messageBody:
I am starting to remember a bit more now. I think there are 2 quests there
- one with the Marshall or Sheriff and the other with the Druid who grows
the jum jum? You have my curiosity piqued - I may have to go back and take
a closer look. I found 2 more cases of jumjum juice.

Snyak.
-----Original Message-----
From: Andrew Palmer [mailto:apalmer@...]
Sent: Wednesday, June 02, 1999 2:23 PM
To: 'warriors_eq@onelist.com'
Subject: Re: [warriors_eq] SOW rings?

From: Andrew Palmer <apalmer@...>

Well the ring you get in rivervale is the squad ring..
it has 1 charge of greater heal and then you have to get it
recharged
again.
No that is not the SoW ring
